c speaker đã dành thời gian hỗ trợ chương trình.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cám ơn các nhà tài trợ đã hỗ trợ tài chính và quà tặng cho sự kiện.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hẹn gặp lại quý anh chị vào Nha Trang WordPress Meetup tháng 9/2024</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-42.jpg\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" data-id=\"1261\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-42-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1261\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-42-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-42-300x200.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-42-768x513.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-42.jpg 1434w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-41-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" data-id=\"1262\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-41-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1262\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-41-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-41-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-41-1-768x513.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-41-1.jpg 1434w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-17.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" data-id=\"1236\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-17-1024x683.jpg\" a